<h1>New stock buyback available</h1>

<p>
  We're excited to inform you that a new stock buyback has opened for <%= @tender_offer.company.name %>.
  This is an opportunity for you to potentially sell some or all of your shares.
</p>

<p>
  Here are the key details of the tender offer:
</p>

<dl>
  <dt>Offer start date</dt>
  <dd><%= @tender_offer.starts_at.to_fs(:long_date) %></dd>
  <dt>Offer end date</dt>
  <dd><%= @tender_offer.ends_at.to_fs(:long_date) %></dd>
  <dt>Starting (minimum) valuation</dt>
  <dd><%= money_format(@tender_offer.minimum_valuation) %></dd>
  <dt>Total offer amount (<b>"Total Gross Proceeds"</b>)</dt>
  <dd><%= cents_format(@tender_offer.total_amount_in_cents) %></dd>
</dl>

<hr>

<p>
  <strong>
    This offer is time-sensitive and will close on <%= @tender_offer.ends_at.to_fs(:long_date) %>.
    Make sure to review and submit your bid before the deadline if you wish to participate.
  </strong>
</p>

<%= link_to "Learn more & participate",
            "#{PROTOCOL}://#{DOMAIN}/equity/tender_offers/#{@tender_offer.external_id}",
            class: "button" %>
